=Yi Jing 義淨 (635-713)=
Buddhist monk who traveled to India by sea route

=Works=
* 大唐西域求法高僧傳
* 南海寄歸內法傳


=Literature=
==Translations==
* Latika Lahiri: Chinese Monks in India. Biography of Eminent Monks who went to the Western World in search of the Law during the Great T'ang Dynasty. Delhi: Motilal Banarsidass, 1986
* J. Takakusu: A Record of the Buddhist Religion as Practised in India and the Malay Archipelago. Oxford: Clarendon Press, 1896 [[@http://www.archive.org/download/recordofbuddhist00ichi/recordofbuddhist00ichi.pdf|PDF]] 